{"tid":123444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥指新移民是寶貴人力資源","createTime":"2017-02-17T01:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T01:35:09.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10e9b4094e11d78bf9f39b4eb928a5f290743877","tid":123444,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:10:39.000Z","msg":"政務司長林鄭月娥指，自回歸以來有八十三萬新移民來港，當中九成八都是港人內地配偶或子女，因此單程證政策是家庭團聚政策，有存在必要。她又指，新移民是本港近年主要人口增長來源，來港人口年齡平均三十三歲，八成有中學以上學歷，是本港寶貴人力資源。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，本港面對人口老化以及勞動力下降的問題，未來會研究如何鼓勵婦女及年長人士投身勞動市場，增加勞動力。"},{"pid":"6bd8a42bf5696ae8da4af06492f165433c7d7293","tid":123444,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:12:05.000Z","msg":"中學程度有撚用咩"},{"pid":"eae51b15a2abfc87dc679c32c5d45c4fed9da5fd","tid":123444,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:17:21.000Z","msg":"淋病"},{"pid":"5238be09ffea65b945b9c5d139a312686401ed83","tid":123444,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:19:32.000Z","msg":"平均三十三歲+中學學歷，香港成地都係啦，去望下啱啱俾HSBC炒果班人都唔止中學啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538937c8658f78b311e34b7c1394583b6408e537","tid":123444,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:19:37.000Z","msg":"真係多撚謝哂"},{"pid":"11520dc438598b33ea7fa65cf39986ad82c553f5","tid":123444,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:19:58.000Z","msg":"屌啦星"},{"pid":"48a38b8ad29baed1eca8a9fdccc1072470c693e6","tid":123444,"uid":61906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:21:00.000Z","msg":"正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0963e27171c32f3692335acc6818d60ca379d0a6","tid":123444,"